synonyms.synonym: Mitogen-activated protein kinase kinase kinase kinase 6

protein.general_function: Involved in small GTPase regulator activity
protein.specific_function: Serine/threonine kinase that may play a role in the response to environmental stress. Appears to act upstream of the JUN N-terminal pathway. May play a role in the development of the brain
